Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.37,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(1069,149)}『１  愉悦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.37,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(1034,158)}２  温柔的双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.37,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(997,167)}３  开朗的气氛』
